<style>
    body {
        visibility: hidden;
        opacity: 0;
        transition: opacity 0.5s ease-in-out;
    }
</style>
<body>
    {{> ../components/header}}

    <main>
        <section class="hero-banner">
            <div class="overlay">
                <div class="banner-content">
                    <h1>Services</h1>
                    {{!-- <p>Primary care and mental health care, all at Rosewell.</p> --}}
                    <p>Primary care and mental health, centered on you. <br> Expert help, easy access.</p>
                    <div class="banner-buttons">
                        <a href="https://practice.kareo.com/rosewell-healthcare" class="btn primary">Schedule Appointment</a>
                        <a href="instructions.html" class="btn secondary">Learn more</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        
        <section class="service-section">
            <div id="primaryCareDescription" class="description">
                <img src="./img/primary-care-icon.png" alt="Primary Care" class="service-icon">
                <h2>Primary Care Services</h2>
                <p>At <strong>Rosewell Healthcare</strong>, we provide comprehensive primary care services to help you maintain your overall health and well-being. Whether you need routine check-ups, preventive care, chronic disease management, or treatment for common illnesses, our dedicated healthcare professionals are here to support you. We focus on personalized, patient-centered care to ensure you receive the best treatment for your unique needs.</p>
                <p><strong>Our primary care services include:</strong></p>
                <ul class="service-list">
                    <li>Annual wellness exams & preventive screenings</li>
                    <li>Chronic disease management (diabetes, hypertension, etc.)</li>
                    <li>Acute illness treatment (cold, flu, infections)</li>
                    <li>Immunizations & vaccinations</li>
                    <li>Women's health services</li>
                    <li>Medication management</li>
                </ul>
                <p>We are committed to providing high-quality, compassionate care to every patient. <a href="https://practice.kareo.com/rosewell-healthcare">Schedule an appointment</a> today.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="service-section">
            <div id="mentalHealthDescription" class="description">
                <img src="./img/mental-health-icon.png" alt="Mental Health" class="service-icon">
                <h2>Mental Health Services</h2>
                <p>Your mental well-being is just as important as your physical health. Our mental health services provide compassionate support and evidence-based treatments to help you navigate life's challenges. Whether you're experiencing stress, anxiety, depression, or other mental health concerns, we are here to help with personalized care.</p>
                <p><strong>Our mental health services include:</strong></p>
                <ul class="service-list">
                    <li>Anxiety & depression management</li>
                    <li>Stress & burnout support</li>
                    <li>Therapy & counseling referrals</li>
                    <li>Medication management for mental health conditions</li>
                    <li>Holistic and integrative approaches to well-being</li>
                </ul>
                <p>At <strong>Rosewell Healthcare</strong>, we believe in treating the whole person -- mind and body. </p>
                <p></p><a href="https://practice.kareo.com/rosewell-healthcare">Book an appointment</a> today to start your journey to better health.
                <p></p>If you a need instructions or detailed steps, <a href="instructions.html">follow this link</a>.
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Footer Component -->
        {{> ../components/footer}}
        
        
